{"word":"H8176 - שָׁעַר - shâʻar - shaw-ar' - Think","slug":"H8176","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁעַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâʻar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-ar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Think"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E2;&#x05E8; - sha&#x0302;&#x201B;ar</b> - <i>shaw-ar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>split</i> or <i>open</i>, that is, (literally, but only as denominative from <a href=\"#/H8179\">H8179</a>) to <i>act as gate keeper</i> (see <a href=\"#/H7778\">H7778</a>); (figuratively) to <i>estimate: - </i>think."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8180\">H8180</a>"}]}